title: GoPro: Southeast Asia Barrels with Alex Gray - GoPro of the World August Winner
description:
Alex gets pitted in an undisclosed location in Southeast Asia and takes home $1,000, a GoPro HERO4, and a year subscription to Surfline.

Shot 100% on the HERO4® camera 

Music
Yamantaka//Sonic Titan
"Hoshi Neko"
